{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"39695-young-or-old","title":"Young or Old?","description":"A little boy is old enough to tie his shoes, but too young to help his father paint the house. He is old enough to feed himself, but too young to help his mother cook. Is he too young, or too old?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Shannon David"],"illustrators":["Shailja Jain Chougule"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/39695-young-or-old"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/384646/size3/f8f79bcb3795b4c076d7650f0c04430b.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/384646/size6/f8f79bcb3795b4c076d7650f0c04430b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74934/size6/c0837da56b54fc7556d9c4be116755c6.jpg","text":"\"May I ride your bicycle?\" I asked Didi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74936/size6/b386e9be2342d7553f8307139c5a0219.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Didi said. \"You’re too young to ride a bike.\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74938/size6/5181b988981cd692d514f481fe63dc57.jpg","text":"\"Didi, can you start the water pump for me?\" I asked.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74953/size6/af6fc1eecdc9319732395efdf00c14d7.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Didi replied. \"You’re old \nenough to do it yourself.\"","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74942/size6/a0ff38027d99cac00c37b1f02dba32c2.jpg","text":"\"Ma, may I help you cut the vegetables?\" I asked.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74944/size6/c522caf492e39ad785b1687d587533da.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Ma said. \"You’re too young to use a knife.\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74951/size6/307840970b700ed817375835901fecd7.jpg","text":"\"Ma, can you please feed me my lunch?\" I asked.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74950/size6/9d23fde498f2de362cf72e85de530c76.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Ma said. \"You’re old enough \nto feed yourself.\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74955/size6/94a8042fd337736095e7d912fd0a7657.jpg","text":"\"May I help paint \nthe wall?\" I asked.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74962/size6/13b3ed2e11e9a34115edb726d7feabd4.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Pa said. \"You’re too young for this.\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74963/size6/b6c63fffd2ab80550fed61a22cbb7457.jpg","text":"\"Can you please help me \nput my shoes on?\" I asked Ma.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74981/size6/20ca39e25a3a9cd874487a313ff53215.jpg","text":"\"No,\" Ma said. \"You’re old enough \nto put your shoes on yourself.\"","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74980/size6/ff082292879937c3b2dd5cf065ed914c.jpg","text":"I was confused.  I thought to myself, \nAm I too old, or too young?","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74978/size6/cd40c186cc4c1363dd55fb2c019f9565.jpg","text":"15/20","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74979/size6/7ecc11dd3f2b1c5053a85e2df994bc0f.jpg","text":"16/20","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74977/size6/15e64c7fee3f554ff9fc1fe40f22486a.jpg","text":"One day, I found Ma's earring under the bed.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74976/size6/0afbaf99f7909d03a1b789435d33fe05.jpg","text":"\"I’ve been looking for this \nfor ages!\" Ma said.","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74975/size6/4c4d4fe10f57811a8fc76389067737d3.jpg","text":"Everyone celebrated. \"You're so grown-up!\" they said.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74974/size6/1d43d5055d0bb90ded3e8cbb9172207d.jpg","text":"But I'm still confused. \nAm I too old or too young?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":170}}